{{Sagittarius}} Sagittarius 4 is the 4th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 4th day of Sagittarius, and it is a Thursday. It corresponds to ISO week 1, weekday 4.
Its informal Japanese name is 1宮4日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 4|Chapter 4]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152024}}.
[[Category:Days with weekday Thursday]] [[Category:Days 4 of the Gaian calendar]] [[Category:Days of Sagittarius]] {{DEFAULTSORT:01宮04日}}
