{{Sagittarius}} Sagittarius 5 is the 5th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 5th day of Sagittarius, and it is a Friday. It corresponds to ISO week 1, weekday 5.
Its informal Japanese name is 1宮5日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 5|Chapter 5]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152025}}.
