{{Sagittarius}} Sagittarius 7 is the 7th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 7th day of Sagittarius, and it is a Sunday. It corresponds to ISO week 1, weekday 7.
Its informal Japanese name is 1宮7日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 7|Chapter 7]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152027}}.
