{{Sagittarius}} Sagittarius 10 is the 10th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 10th day of Sagittarius, and it is a Wednesday. It corresponds to ISO week 2, weekday 3.
Its informal Japanese name is 1宮10日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 10|Chapter 10]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152030}}.
