{{Sagittarius}} Sagittarius 12 is the 12th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 12th day of Sagittarius, and it is a Friday. It corresponds to ISO week 2, weekday 5.
Its informal Japanese name is 1宮12日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 12|Chapter 12]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152032}}.
