{{Sagittarius}} Sagittarius 14 is the 14th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 14th day of Sagittarius, and it is a Sunday. It corresponds to ISO week 2, weekday 7.
Its informal Japanese name is 1宮14日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 14|Chapter 14]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152034}}.
