{{Sagittarius}} Sagittarius 17 is the 17th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 17th day of Sagittarius, and it is a Wednesday. It corresponds to ISO week 3, weekday 3.
Its informal Japanese name is 1宮17日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 17|Chapter 17]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152037}}.
