{{Sagittarius}} Sagittarius 19 is the 19th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 19th day of Sagittarius, and it is a Friday. It corresponds to ISO week 3, weekday 5.
Its informal Japanese name is 1宮19日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 19|Chapter 19]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152039}}.
