{{Sagittarius}} Sagittarius 25 is the 25th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 25th day of Sagittarius, and it is a Thursday. It corresponds to ISO week 4, weekday 4.
Its informal Japanese name is 1宮25日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 25|Chapter 25]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152045}}.
