{{Sagittarius}} Sagittarius 27 is the 27th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 27th day of Sagittarius, and it is a Saturday. It corresponds to ISO week 4, weekday 6.
Its informal Japanese name is 1宮27日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 27|Chapter 27]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152047}}.
