{{Capricorn}} Capricorn 27 is the 55th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 27th day of Capricorn, and it is a Saturday. It corresponds to ISO week 8, weekday 6.
Its informal Japanese name is 2宮27日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 55|Chapter 55]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152075}}.
