{{Aquarius}} Aquarius 13 is the 69th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 13th day of Aquarius, and it is a Saturday. It corresponds to ISO week 10, weekday 6.
Its informal Japanese name is 3宮13日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 69|Chapter 69]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152089}}.
