{{Aries}} Aries 23 is the 135th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 23rd day of Aries, and it is a Tuesday. It corresponds to ISO week 20, weekday 2.
Its informal Japanese name is 5宮23日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 135|Chapter 135]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152155}}.
