{{Aries}} Aries 26 is the 138th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 26th day of Aries, and it is a Friday. It corresponds to ISO week 20, weekday 5.
Its informal Japanese name is 5宮26日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 138|Chapter 138]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152158}}.
