{{Taurus}} Taurus 1 is the 141st day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 1st day of Taurus, and it is a Monday. It corresponds to ISO week 21, weekday 1.
Its informal Japanese name is 6宮1日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 141|Chapter 141]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152161}}.
