{{Taurus}} Taurus 3 is the 143rd day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 3rd day of Taurus, and it is a Wednesday. It corresponds to ISO week 21, weekday 3.
Its informal Japanese name is 6宮3日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 143|Chapter 143]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152163}}.
