{{Taurus}} Taurus 6 is the 146th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 6th day of Taurus, and it is a Saturday. It corresponds to ISO week 21, weekday 6.
Its informal Japanese name is 6宮6日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 146|Chapter 146]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152166}}.
