{{Taurus}} Taurus 10 is the 150th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 10th day of Taurus, and it is a Wednesday. It corresponds to ISO week 22, weekday 3.
Its informal Japanese name is 6宮10日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 150|Chapter 150]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152170}}.
