{{Taurus}} Taurus 20 is the 160th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 20th day of Taurus, and it is a Saturday. It corresponds to ISO week 23, weekday 6.
Its informal Japanese name is 6宮20日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 160|Chapter 160]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152180}}.
