{{Taurus}} Taurus 23 is the 163rd day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 23rd day of Taurus, and it is a Tuesday. It corresponds to ISO week 24, weekday 2.
Its informal Japanese name is 6宮23日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 163|Chapter 163]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152183}}.
