{{Gemini}} Gemini 9 is the 177th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 9th day of Gemini, and it is a Tuesday. It corresponds to ISO week 26, weekday 2.
Its informal Japanese name is 7宮9日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 177|Chapter 177]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152197}}.
