{{Cancer}} Cancer 5 is the 201st day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 5th day of Cancer, and it is a Friday. It corresponds to ISO week 29, weekday 5.
Its informal Japanese name is 8宮5日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 201|Chapter 201]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152221}}.
