{{Cancer}} Cancer 7 is the 203rd day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 7th day of Cancer, and it is a Sunday. It corresponds to ISO week 29, weekday 7.
Its informal Japanese name is 8宮7日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 203|Chapter 203]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152223}}.
