{{Cancer}} Cancer 12 is the 208th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 12th day of Cancer, and it is a Friday. It corresponds to ISO week 30, weekday 5.
Its informal Japanese name is 8宮12日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 208|Chapter 208]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152228}}.
