{{Cancer}} Cancer 23 is the 219th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 23rd day of Cancer, and it is a Tuesday. It corresponds to ISO week 32, weekday 2.
Its informal Japanese name is 8宮23日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 219|Chapter 219]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152239}}.
