{{Cancer}} Cancer 25 is the 221st day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 25th day of Cancer, and it is a Thursday. It corresponds to ISO week 32, weekday 4.
Its informal Japanese name is 8宮25日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 221|Chapter 221]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152241}}.
