{{Cancer}} Cancer 27 is the 223rd day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 27th day of Cancer, and it is a Saturday. It corresponds to ISO week 32, weekday 6.
Its informal Japanese name is 8宮27日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 223|Chapter 223]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152243}}.
