{{Leo}} Leo 3 is the 227th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 3rd day of Leo, and it is a Wednesday. It corresponds to ISO week 33, weekday 3.
Its informal Japanese name is 9宮3日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 227|Chapter 227]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152247}}.
