{{Leo}} Leo 5 is the 229th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 5th day of Leo, and it is a Friday. It corresponds to ISO week 33, weekday 5.
Its informal Japanese name is 9宮5日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 229|Chapter 229]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152249}}.
