{{Leo}} Leo 7 is the 231st day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 7th day of Leo, and it is a Sunday. It corresponds to ISO week 33, weekday 7.
Its informal Japanese name is 9宮7日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 231|Chapter 231]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152251}}.
