{{Leo}} Leo 10 is the 234th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 10th day of Leo, and it is a Wednesday. It corresponds to ISO week 34, weekday 3.
Its informal Japanese name is 9宮10日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 234|Chapter 234]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152254}}.
