{{Leo}} Leo 12 is the 236th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 12th day of Leo, and it is a Friday. It corresponds to ISO week 34, weekday 5.
Its informal Japanese name is 9宮12日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 236|Chapter 236]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152256}}.
