{{Leo}} Leo 16 is the 240th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 16th day of Leo, and it is a Tuesday. It corresponds to ISO week 35, weekday 2.
Its informal Japanese name is 9宮16日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 240|Chapter 240]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152260}}.
