{{Leo}} Leo 23 is the 247th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 23rd day of Leo, and it is a Tuesday. It corresponds to ISO week 36, weekday 2.
Its informal Japanese name is 9宮23日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 247|Chapter 247]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152267}}.
