{{Leo}} Leo 25 is the 249th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 25th day of Leo, and it is a Thursday. It corresponds to ISO week 36, weekday 4.
Its informal Japanese name is 9宮25日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 249|Chapter 249]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152268}}.
