{{Leo}} Leo 27 is the 251st day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 27th day of Leo, and it is a Saturday. It corresponds to ISO week 36, weekday 6.
Its informal Japanese name is 9宮27日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 251|Chapter 251]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152270}}.
