{{Virgo}} Virgo 5 is the 257th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 5th day of Virgo, and it is a Friday. It corresponds to ISO week 37, weekday 5.
Its informal Japanese name is 10宮5日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 257|Chapter 257]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152276}}.
