{{Virgo}} Virgo 18 is the 270th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 18th day of Virgo, and it is a Thursday. It corresponds to ISO week 39, weekday 4.
Its informal Japanese name is 10宮18日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 270|Chapter 270]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152289}}.
