{{Virgo}} Virgo 20 is the 272nd day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 20th day of Virgo, and it is a Saturday. It corresponds to ISO week 39, weekday 6.
Its informal Japanese name is 10宮20日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 272|Chapter 272]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152291}}.
