{{Virgo}} Virgo 23 is the 275th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 23rd day of Virgo, and it is a Tuesday. It corresponds to ISO week 40, weekday 2.
Its informal Japanese name is 10宮23日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 275|Chapter 275]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152294}}.
