{{Virgo}} Virgo 25 is the 277th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 25th day of Virgo, and it is a Thursday. It corresponds to ISO week 40, weekday 4.
Its informal Japanese name is 10宮25日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 277|Chapter 277]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152296}}.
