{{Virgo}} Virgo 27 is the 279th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 27th day of Virgo, and it is a Saturday. It corresponds to ISO week 40, weekday 6.
Its informal Japanese name is 10宮27日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 279|Chapter 279]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152298}}.
