{{Libra}} Libra 3 is the 283rd day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 3rd day of Libra, and it is a Wednesday. It corresponds to ISO week 41, weekday 3.
Its informal Japanese name is 11宮3日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 283|Chapter 283]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152302}}.
