{{Libra}} Libra 5 is the 285th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 5th day of Libra, and it is a Friday. It corresponds to ISO week 41, weekday 5.
Its informal Japanese name is 11宮5日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 285|Chapter 285]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152304}}.
