{{Libra}} Libra 7 is the 287th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 7th day of Libra, and it is a Sunday. It corresponds to ISO week 41, weekday 7.
Its informal Japanese name is 11宮7日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 287|Chapter 287]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152306}}.
