{{Libra}} Libra 10 is the 290th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 10th day of Libra, and it is a Wednesday. It corresponds to ISO week 42, weekday 3.
Its informal Japanese name is 11宮10日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 290|Chapter 290]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152309}}.
