{{Libra}} Libra 12 is the 292nd day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 12th day of Libra, and it is a Friday. It corresponds to ISO week 42, weekday 5.
Its informal Japanese name is 11宮12日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 292|Chapter 292]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152311}}.
