{{Libra}} Libra 16 is the 296th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 16th day of Libra, and it is a Tuesday. It corresponds to ISO week 43, weekday 2.
Its informal Japanese name is 11宮16日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 296|Chapter 296]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152315}}.
