{{Libra}} Libra 18 is the 298th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 18th day of Libra, and it is a Thursday. It corresponds to ISO week 43, weekday 4.
Its informal Japanese name is 11宮18日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 298|Chapter 298]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152317}}.
