{{Libra}} Libra 20 is the 300th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 20th day of Libra, and it is a Saturday. It corresponds to ISO week 43, weekday 6.
Its informal Japanese name is 11宮20日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 300|Chapter 300]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152319}}.
