{{Scorpio}} Scorpio 27 is the 335th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 27th day of Scorpio, and it is a Saturday. It corresponds to ISO week 48, weekday 6.
Its informal Japanese name is 12宮27日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 335|Chapter 335]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152354}}.
