{{Ophiuchus}} Ophiuchus 1 is the 337th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 1st day of Ophiuchus, and it is a Monday. It corresponds to ISO week 49, weekday 1.
Its informal Japanese name is 13宮1日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 337|Chapter 337]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152356}}.
