{{Ophiuchus}} Ophiuchus 3 is the 339th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 3rd day of Ophiuchus, and it is a Wednesday. It corresponds to ISO week 49, weekday 3.
Its informal Japanese name is 13宮3日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 339|Chapter 339]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152358}}.
