{{Ophiuchus}} Ophiuchus 5 is the 341st day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 5th day of Ophiuchus, and it is a Friday. It corresponds to ISO week 49, weekday 5.
Its informal Japanese name is 13宮5日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 341|Chapter 341]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152360}}.
