{{Ophiuchus}} Ophiuchus 7 is the 343rd day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 7th day of Ophiuchus, and it is a Sunday. It corresponds to ISO week 49, weekday 7.
Its informal Japanese name is 13宮7日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 343|Chapter 343]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152362}}.
