{{Ophiuchus}} Ophiuchus 11 is the 347th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 11th day of Ophiuchus, and it is a Thursday. It corresponds to ISO week 50, weekday 4.
Its informal Japanese name is 13宮11日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 347|Chapter 347]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152366}}.
