{{Ophiuchus}} Ophiuchus 13 is the 349th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 13th day of Ophiuchus, and it is a Saturday. It corresponds to ISO week 50, weekday 6.
Its informal Japanese name is 13宮13日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 349|Chapter 349]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152368}}.
