{{Ophiuchus}} Ophiuchus 15 is the 351st day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is the 15th day of Ophiuchus, and it is a Monday. It corresponds to ISO week 51, weekday 1.
Its informal Japanese name is 13宮15日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 351|Chapter 351]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152370}}.
