{{Horus}} Horus 1 is the 365th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is an intercalary day, the 1st of the 7 days of Horus. It falls on a Monday in intercalary week 53.
Its informal Japanese name is 14宮1日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 365|Chapter 365]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152384}}.
