{{Horus}} Horus 2 is the 366th day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is an intercalary day, the 2nd of the 7 days of Horus. It falls on a Tuesday in intercalary week 53.
Its informal Japanese name is 14宮2日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 366|Chapter 366]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152385}}.
