{{Horus}} Horus 7 is the 371st day of the year in the [[Gaian calendar]]. It is an intercalary day, the 7th of the 7 days of Horus. It falls on a Sunday in intercalary week 53.
Its informal Japanese name is 14宮7日.
On this day, [[Gaiad chapter 371|Chapter 371]] of the [[Gaiad]] is read.
To see structured data on this date see {{q|Q152390}}.
